    "body": "In the current chunked ORC reader, only row counts of the top-level columns are considered when splitting the loaded stripes into subsets of stripes to avoid decoding more than 2B rows, which is cudf column size limit. The nested children columns are not taken into account.\r\n\r\nWe should consider row count at all nested levels.",
